15th — You will see an Exhibition that has been witnessed and endorsed by —

     PRESIDENT ARTHUR AND CABINET;

     GEN. SHERIDAN AND STAFF;

     GENERALS SHERMAN, CROOK, MILES, CARR, ETC;

     RISTORI, PATTI, NEVADA, BOOTH, IRVING, BARRETT;

     BENNETT, WATTERSON, CHILDS, VANDERBILT,

     BELMONT, DREXEL,

   And tens of thousands of well-informed people in EVERY WALK OF LIFE.
